### 1. Test Health Endpoint
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health
Accept: application/json

### 2. List All Campaigns
GET http://localhost:8080/api/campaigns
Accept: application/json

### 3. Create a New Campaign
POST http://localhost:8080/api/campaigns
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "chain_campaign_id": 1,
  "owner_address": "0x1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef12345678",
  "title": "Bantu Sekolah Pelosok",
  "short_description": "Donasi untuk sekolah rusak",
  "long_description": "Sekolah ini rusak sejak tahun lalu dan butuh dana untuk atap.",
  "category": "education",
  "target_amount": 500.5,
  "cover_image_url": "https://example.com/image.jpg",
  "beneficiary_name": "SDN 1 Pelosok",
  "location": "Desa Terpencil, Indonesia",
  "expected_impact": "100 siswa bisa kembali belajar dengan nyaman"
}

### 4. Create a Donation
POST http://localhost:8080/api/donations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "campaign_id": "REPLACE_WITH_UUID_FROM_ABOVE",
  "donor_address": "0xABCDEF1234567890ABCDEF1234567890ABCDEF12",
  "amount": 10.5,
  "tx_hash": "0xabcdef1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef1234567890"
}
